<F P=102>  LD1412194193 Kiev Radio Ukraine World Service in Ukrainian 
1600 GMT 14 Dec 93 </F>

<F P=103> LD1412194193 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev Radio Ukraine World Service </F>


