Language: <F P=105> Ukrainian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] During the past few days Army General of Ukraine 
Vitaliy Radetskyy, minister of defense, has visited units and 
facilities of the strategic missile troops deployed on the 
territory of our state. The existing problems have been 
thoroughly analyzed with scientists and specialists during these 
