  [Excerpt] The 10th PRC airliner hijacked to Taiwan this 
year departed Taoyuan Chiang Kai-shek Airport for Hsiamen 
[Xiamen] at 1823 local time [1023 GMT]. Although our government 
reiterated that the principle of separately handling hijackers 
and airplanes would remain unchanged, this time around relevant 
