<H3> <TI>   Communist Spokesman Rejects Boncayao Brigade </TI></H3>
<H4>   Further on Official's Disavowal </H4>
<F P=102> BK2812084793 Quezon City PTV-4 Television Network in Tagalog 
0500 GMT 28 Dec 93 </F>

<F P=103> BK2812084793 </F>
<F P=104>  Quezon City PTV-4 Television Network </F>


