<H3> <TI>   Follow-up to Phalangist Office Bombing </TI></H3>
<H4>   Composite Picture of Suspect Circulated </H4>
<F P=102> NC2912182593 Beirut Voice of Lebanon in Arabic 1715 GMT 29 
Dec 93 </F>

<F P=103> NC2912182593 </F>
<F P=104>  Beirut Voice of Lebanon </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The Army Command, acting on a notice from the 
Military Prosecution Office, today circulated a composite 
picture of a suspect in the bombing of the Phalangist 
headquarters. [see item NC2012164193 in previous Terrorism 
Report] The Army Command asked citizens who have information 
about the person identified in the composite picture to apply in 
person at or telephone the Military Prosecution Office at any 
time. 
  Added to the composite picture is the following description: 
He is between 27 to 30 years old with a round face and brownish 
complexion. His hair is black, combed back. He has a full head 
of hair. He has a broad and swollen chin. He is approximately 
175 cm high and is heavily built. 

</TEXT>

