<F P=106> [By ITAR-TASS Sharip Asuyev] </F>
  [Text] Groznyy, North Caucasus December 24 -- The Chechen 
Republic has announced it is ready to receive the helicopter 
with four terrorists and hostages on board and guarantee their 
complete safety, if the kidnappers agree to exchange the 
children taken hostages in Rostov on Thursday are exchanged for 
