the terrorists with a fully fueled aircraft to fly to any 
destination they may choose. 
  Saipudi Khasanov stressed that he was ready to go on board 
himself to free the children. Russian authorities negotiating 
with the terrorists have been notified about this proposal of 
the Groznyy authorities prompted by their concern about the 
lives of the Rostov schoolchildren. 

