certain flying experience which is proved by the demand to 
provide flight documents and accumulators. [passage omitted] 
  The helicopter unexpectedly took off from Mineralnyye Vody 
on 
Friday, but then returned back. 
  It became known that special commando groups were flying 
after the helicopter with terrorists all the way from 
Rostov-on-Don. 

