<H3> <TI>   Palestinian Oppositionists Form Alliance of `Forces' </TI></H3>
<H4>   To `Confront' Gaza-Jericho </H4>
<F P=102> NC0601165794 Cairo MENA in Arabic 1630 GMT 6 Jan 94 </F>
