  [Text] Damascus, 6 Jan (MENA)--The 10 Palestinian factions 
based in Damascus, which oppose the PLO, have declared the 
formation of the Alliance of the Palestinian Forces [tahaluf 
al-quwa al-filastinyah] with the aim of confronting the 
Gaza-Jericho agreement. The Palestinian oppositionists also 
declared that they are preparing a popular conference to marshal 
