<F P=102>  TA0201060894 Ankara Turkiye Radyolari Network in Turkish 
0530 GMT 2 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA0201060894 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara Turkiye Radyolari Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Turkish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Terrorists have killed eight people near the Mardin 
District of the Diyarbakir-Elazig highway. 
  According to information issued by Unal Erkan, state of 
emergency region governor, terrorists stopped two buses, which 
were on their way from Diyarbakir to Elazig, at 4 km from Mardin 
around 2100. Terrorists abducted eight persons from the buses, 
brought them to a rural area, and killed them. Security forces' 
operations are under way in the region. 

</TEXT>

